iangjiang New Area|Liangjiang]] of [[Chongqing]]), which is also the second state-level new development area in East China.<ref>{{cite web|last=Wang|first=Shen|title=China approves Zhoushan Archipelago New Area to promote oceanic economy|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english2010/china/2011-07/07/c_13971902.htm|publisher=Xinhua|accessdate=22 January 2014}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{New Area}}\n{{Zhejiang}}\n\n[[Category:New areas (China)]]\n[[Category:Zhoushan]]\n", "text_old": "{{For|the city|Zhoushan}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- Basic info  ---------------->\n|name                   = {{raise|0.2em|Zhoushan Archipelago New Area}}\n|native_name            = {{lower|0.1em|{{nobold|{{lang|zh-hans|\u821f\u5c71\u7fa4\u5c9b\u65b0\u533a}}}}}}\n|official_name          = \n|other_name             =\n|nickname               = \n|settlement_type        =[[State-level new areas of the People's Republic of China|State-level new area]]\n|total_type             = <!-- to set a non-standard label for total area and population rows -->\n|motto                  =\n<!-- images and maps  ----------->\n|image_skyline          = \n|imagesize              = \n|image_caption          = \n|image_flag             = \n|flag_size              =\n|image_seal             = \n|seal_size              =\n|image_shield           = \n|shield_size            =\n|image_blank_emblem     =\n|blank_emblem_type      =\n|blank_emblem_size      =\n|image_map              = \n|mapsize                = \n|map_caption            = \n|image_map1             = \n|mapsize1               = \n|map_caption1           = \n|image_dot_map          =\n|dot_mapsize            =\n|dot_map_caption        =\n|dot_x =  |dot_y =\n|pushpin_map =\n|pushpin_label_position = <!-- the position of the pushpin label: left, right, top, bottom, none -->\n|pushpin_map_caption    =\n|pushpin_mapsize        =\n<!-- Location ------------------>\n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name = [[China|People's Repub